{"type": "article", "id": 57987, "title": "Marc Jacobs 和迪士尼推出“米老鼠”主题联名，WPP 暂停招聘 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2018-11-05T04:02:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 701, "name": "商业"}, {"id": 3940, "name": "圣诞季"}, {"id": 111, "name": "迪士尼"}, {"id": 1318, "name": "WPP"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181105111848DqiI4SdOgpaTEQPF.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4301531140146094?sudaref=login.sina.com.cn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">彭于晏成为日本彩妆品牌 KATE 凯朵品牌代言人。</a></strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105111939r1fcRLqCswFlBkby.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499023\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4301668713383270?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>太平鸟和宝洁合作推出 “Me and My 嘻习洗戏”系列，</strong></a>将宝洁旗下众多品的 Logo 与服装相结合，该系列包括外套、T恤、卫衣等。还发布了 “ONE DAY AT HOME” 的 Lookbook，创意不错。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105112035xA1Q0EnXKFSzaR8G.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.818357\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105112533HF07uangfQwDU8rO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.224638\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811051123119v4yxB5Y7AP10cSm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.224609\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105112617bOSMVFRqsJKYt971.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.224609\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>美国歌手 Pharrell Williams 将和 Chanel 带来最新合作项目，<strong><a href=\"https://go.hsnob.co/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dazeddigital.com%2Ffashion%2Farticle%2F42043%2F1%2Fpharrell-is-designing-a-collection-for-chanel\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Williams 亲手设计了黄色 Chanel 帽衫等产品。</a></strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105112659ngrJPCMEpQd1aRlX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>迪士尼庆祝米老鼠 90 岁生日，<a href=\"https://style.disney.com/fashion/2018/07/10/mickey-mouse-marc-jacobs-exclusive/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>和 Marc Jacobs 合作推出一系列富有街头感的休闲服饰。</strong></a>&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105112728gZQro0WYTBJ1nRfm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105112739NL2CiXaIwu3OxoyG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105112803vfekcad89nZIQDm0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105112751s1U3GJ7yukNZWaBw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p>SK-II 和艺术家 Karan Singh 推出的 “PiteraWonderland” 主题限量版神仙水已上市，<strong><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4301959865079176?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">形象代言人窦靖童出演了广告片</a>。</strong>和该系列的产品设计一样，片中也运用了不少波普元素，色调挺鲜艳。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=x0778r21f8v\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4301521338380575?https://m.weibo.cn/status/4301521338380575?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>OPPO 发布了另一个夜色系列广告片“夜的声光集”，</strong></a>代言人陈伟霆和王俊凯参与，他们并没有出镜，而是用声音讲述了各自故乡的夜色美景。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=q0778dhi3v3\"></iframe> </figure> </div><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=d0777qnmal3\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4301521338380575?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>英国连锁快餐 Greggs 将自己的 Logo 翻转了，</strong></a>这是家位于英国纽卡斯尔的 Fenwick 圣诞橱窗对面的店铺。人们在橱窗里就可以看到原本正确的 Logo ，自拍时候也能抢镜，免费宣传选的位置不错。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105113039xTfLl9tyh4QDZVgq.png\" data-ratio=\"0.531091\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p>人们在 Twitter 上批评 KFC 的薯条不好吃，KFC 就势推出了新薯条的广告，<strong><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/why-kfc-turned-a-tweet-from-one-of-its-biggest-critics-into-a-u-k-ad-campaign/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">形式和网友的吐槽一模一样。</a></strong><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105113629ubmzRLKtsivhjB9q.png\" data-ratio=\"0.634744\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105113611Z1wLF5fbMSmpjydC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p><a href=\"https://adage.com/article/digital/apple-s-itp-2-starting-a-huge-impact-advertisers/315476/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>在最新版本的 Apple Safari 浏览器中嵌入了反跟踪功能，</strong></a>阻止 cookie 在开放网络中工作，这使得以后计算数字广告的投资回报更加困难了。</p><p>对接下来盈利信心不足的 WPP ，<a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/news/2018/11/04/wpp-freeze-recruitment-until-early-2019-amid-gloomy-profit-forecast%E8%AF%B7%208%20%E5%AE%B6%E5%A8%B1%E4%B9%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%88%9B%E4%BD%9C%E7%BB%8F%E9%AA%8C%E3%80%82\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>宣布将暂停招聘直到 2019 年初。</strong></a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/amazon-kicks-off-the-holiday-season-with-a-global-ad-starring-its-joyful-singing-boxes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>今年圣诞季亚马逊的“唱歌盒子“回归，</strong></a>快递盒上的微笑脸将会在广告片 “Can you feel it” 里真的笑起来，还唱起了歌。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/agencies/over-100-agencies-are-rallying-behind-this-bold-campaign-to-end-sexual-harassment-in-advertising/\" rel=\"nofollow\">戛纳创意节再次进行了调整，</a></strong>新增设两个狮子：“Creative Strategy Lion（创意策略狮）” 和 “Entertainment Lion for Sports（运动娱乐狮）”。 Product Design 奖被分解成 Design（设计狮） 和 Innovation（创新狮）。同时，<strong><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/agencies/cannes-and-medialink-to-offer-marketers-exclusive-content-creation-education-at-2019-festival/\" rel=\"nofollow\">戛纳还和战略顾问 MediaLink 达成了合作，</a></strong>邀请 8 家娱乐公司分享内容创作经验。<br></p><p>题图来自：迪士尼官网</p>"}